  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The VERTIGO study is likely to help determine characteristics of different types of vertigo
      in patients presenting in the Ear Nose &amp; Throat (ENT) clinics with complaints of dizziness.
      Moreover, it will also help to develop an understanding about the current management
      practices of this condition at local level.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
